name: NWBrowser.Result.Change
desc: Ways in which discovered services can change between specific results.

items.name: case identical
items.desc: No change was detected for the result.

items.name: case removed(NWBrowser.Result)
items.desc: A previously discovered result was removed.

items.name: case changed(old: NWBrowser.Result, new: NWBrowser.Result, flags: NWBrowser.Result.Change.Flags)
items.desc: A result changed properties but was not removed.

items.name: struct NWBrowser.Result.Change.Flags
items.desc: Flags providing details about a change in a discovered service.

items.name: init(between: NWBrowser.Result?, NWBrowser.Result?)
items.desc: Initializes a change between two results.
